<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="60" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="60">Geographical distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="60">
From the few specimens available this species appears to have a northern distribution (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Distributions of collection records of Bembix spp.: a Bembix albata b Bembix albicapilla c Bembix albofasciata d Bembix anomalipes e Bembix arnoldi f Bembix atrospinosa." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11851" pageId="7" pageNumber="60">Fig. 2d</figureCitation>
), not having been recorded south of Zimbabwe.
</paragraph>
